Duvidas

- Front e Back ligarem-se à mesma DB?
- Fazer o backend de FO ou BO?
- Que API externa a consumir?

Rotas FO:

- GET /products/:id
- GET /products
- GET /products? (Filtros)
- GET /profile (AUTH JWT)
- GET /cart
- GET /about
- POST /register (EMAIL)
- POST /logout
- POST /logout?all=true (logout de todos?)
- POST /cart (EMAIL)
- PATCH /profile (EMAIL)
- PATCH /cart

Rotas BO: 
- GET /customers
- GET /products
- GET /products/collections
- GET /products/:id
- PATCH /products/:id
- PATCH /customers

